The paper presents a method for automatically generating numerical invariants for imperative programs, which involves approximating loop behavior and computing an abstract meaning of each part of the program. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Logic in Computer Science (cs.LO), Programming Languages (cs.PL), Software Engineering (cs.SE), Formal Languages and Automata Theory (cs.FL), or Symbolic Computation (cs.SC) sub-categories.
